<H2 class="bacg">Corporate Workplace Executives.</H2><p class="bacg">&nbsp;Corporate Workplace Executive teams partner with the lines of business to drive internal space planning and optimize the current real estate portfolio to meet business objectives.</p>
<br><img src="../images/clear.gif" width="10" height="12" alt="" border="0" /><br>
<H2 class="bacg">Portfolio Management</H2><p class="bacg">&nbsp;integrates delivery of workplace functions (transaction, project management and facility management) within geographic regions. The portfolio management team also ensures that associates and customers are comfortable and shareholder value is maximized through the efficient operation of our facilities.</p>
<br><img src="../images/clear.gif" width="10" height="12" alt="" border="0" /><br>
<H2 class="bacg">Project Management</H2><p class="bacg">&nbsp;leads all projects to build new space and buildings and upgrade existing space including the management of projects executed by outsourced support partners.</p>
